data.description: PRICE REDUCED. Stunning 6-Bedroom Furnished Vacation Home near Disney! This Beautifully decorated home has been completely remodeled and features: over $80,000 in Upgrades;  6-Bedrooms and 4-Bathrooms with plenty of space to accomodate your family and friends;  Gourmet Kitchen with appliances and fixtures;  2 Master Bedrooms, both on the first floor, each of them featuring a wet bar with beautiful cabinetry, as well as private exit to a private backyard, and ample private bathrooms;   Majestic 24-feet tall Vaulted Ceilings, and a 20-feet tall fireplace with 12-Led-lights in the living room;   Open Floorplan concept that creates a spacious and inviting atmosphere;   New Paint and New Flooring throughout the home;  Large Backyard, and a private patio, with ground-spa/pool system hook ups;    Quarter acre lot in short term rental allowed community;   Access to the amenities and facilities of Montego Bay, such as the Pool, the Playground, tennis court, and more.   Prime location just minutes away from Walt Disney World, golf courses, shopping complexes, grocery outlets, the airport, and all the major attractions of the vicinity.   This home is your haven away from home. With private accommodations for all your guests and inviting spaces ideal for hosting gatherings, this residence offers the ultimate fusion of comfort and entertainment. With HOA of only $38/month, $60,000 in yearly long-term rental income, and more as a short-term rental, this home is the perfect investment for landlords and investors. Don’t miss this chance to own a piece of paradise. Contact us today to schedule a viewing or make an offer!
